{"tid":5913,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴打試過發好多關於同以前熟但無一齊到個啲女既夢","createTime":"2016-11-27T06:09:04.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-27T06:25:21.000Z","uid":3824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b11dbe3f80b4df5982ba561465c4e5d74718a7fb","tid":5913,"uid":3824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T06:09:04.000Z","msg":"就算依家同自己女朋友一齊左差唔多七年,<br />\n都重有發啲關於以前無齊到個啲女既夢,<br />\n識左個條女起碼超過10年,<br />\n但係由中五開始已經無聯絡,<br />\nFacebook 好似都俾佢Block 鳩埋,<br />\n應該係問所有以前中學識既朋友都話無佢既消息,<br />\n好似人間蒸發左咁.<br />\n<br />\n最奇怪係whatsapp 都好似無用咁<br />\n可能轉左電話掛.<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思我講到1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都係想睇下有無人會好似我咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"487efc977347c545b2df769944201ec693f86797","tid":5913,"uid":9105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T06:19:07.000Z","msg":"發過同一d以前識既女仔拍拖既夢<br />\n但係自己從來無鍾意過佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59cb35436be87d52703308600bdbc68336159d53","tid":5913,"uid":3824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T06:25:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>發過同一d以前識既女仔拍拖既夢<br />\n但係自己從來無鍾意過佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁個個女仔都幾深刻既<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係始終都係無一齊到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係咁多年都時不時會call up 番我啲記憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}